title: The Football League Show 14.09.2014 PDTV X264
description:
SPORT: The Football League Show
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Sunday 14th September 2014 
Time: 00:25 to 01:45 

Highlights and analysis from the Football League, presented by Manish Bhasin. The week's featured game comes from the Valley as Charlton go head-to-head with Watford. Plus extended highlights from Saturday's early kick-off as Birmingham City meet Leeds United, and the best of the action from Bolton Wanderers against Sheffield Wednesday.
